text: Anna Asheshov (born 8 July 1941) is a British alpine skier. She competed in the women's downhill at the 1964 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1941 births Category:Living people Category:British female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Great Britain Category:Alpine skiers at the 1964 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from London
